{"tid":2222562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"根本無論國際線定本地線 土共都想泛民留任做佢地土共打國際線既彈藥同本地線既替死鬼 點知泛民又貪錢上釣","createTime":"2020-09-29T07:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T00:49:22.000Z","uid":252492,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2431c4e4c498756f04df28de96784271f1a734e1","tid":2222562,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:33:45.000Z","msg":"對外國際 土共要用泛民反對派都支持個議會<br />\n話個議會合法性得到反對派承認 黎打國際線<br />\n<br />\n對本地線<br />\n未來幾年香港經濟仆緊街 政府推乜政策都死<br />\n如果無晒民主派 到時香港經濟一仆街<br />\n政府同親中派無得再賴民主派攪事<br />\n所有矛頭就會集中指向政府同親中派<br />\n分分鐘班淺藍都轉深黃<br />\n<br />\n根本係土共角度當彈藥又好 政治替死鬼又好<br />\n都要有泛民留低 點知泛民班友 特別黃碧雲之流 奶都奶唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da26faac5dafd3d19b1aed952486043e723e1f24","tid":2222562,"uid":283972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b5fea562b7e2300f1338ecdc3004a4799c4376","tid":2222562,"uid":283972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:36:00.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"6b27b98609ac509462543273e8d79090133b4647","tid":2222562,"uid":283972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:36:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81cd738dd1ea242707bafb73c7f5bf27beffadc7","tid":2222562,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661e4056e624f97a0d3eeaa6614df5645f223b71","tid":2222562,"uid":283972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:36:46.000Z","msg":"留的不選"},{"pid":"3551f91c915351a386bd9627dfce6ffc12380366","tid":2222562,"uid":283972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:37:30.000Z","msg":"想要合法性，做戲"},{"pid":"b2e3daf7de6bcac7b010d6281334e7c9daa76d02","tid":22225